Position Summary As the Benefits Analyst you will be responsible for supporting the Senior Analysts, Account Executives and Consulting Team in managing client accounts. Our approach is warm and our relationships are everything with these client groups.


Essential Duties

Collaborate with service providers for the collection, analysis and interpretation of life, disability and health care data;
