The ability to be detailed, analyze data and perform basic mathematical tasks;
A Strong command of MS Excel, Word and PowerPoint;
Excellent verbal and written communication skills;
Prioritizing and handling multiple tasks within deadlines;
Working on a team and independently with minimal supervision makes you happy, as does developing Relationships with service vendors and clients.










