Minimum 3 years of experience in a group benefits environment
BA/BS degree in math, statistics, economics, business, finance or liberal arts or commensurate experience
CEBS designation would be an asset
Consider yourself an expert in the Microsoft Suite and can manage your Outlook inbox with ease
